./.title: Readme
./.body:
Read me
This is a prototype. I have identified a bunch of plugins which could be usful for course content delivery.
Summary

 Structure testing: as shown in this page. The course content is delivered based on weeks.
Video testing: in learning objective, I have shown two different ways of embedding videos. Users can either embed a video through a private link or through YouTube
Math equation testing: in Different Signal section, the equation display is demonstrated.
Code Snippet testing: In section Signal sampling, I show three plugins for displaying codes in Python
Quiz and exercise testing: In section Quiz, I have explored three plugins for designing different quizzes.
